<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl card">
  <header class="card-header">
    <h1 class="title">Training</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Structured study and self-directed learning.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <ul class="space-y-6">

      <li class="work-card">
        <h3 class="work-title">Launch School</h3>
        <p class="work-text">
          A mastery-based software engineering curriculum focused on
          programming fundamentals, problem-solving, Ruby, HTTP, SQL, databases,
          and JavaScript.
        </p>
        <p class="work-text">
          I built several small full-stack applications during the course,
          including a Sinatra todo manager now deployed online.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <%= link_to "See what I studied", launch_school_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>
      </li>

    </ul>
  </section>
</div>
